Package util

Class StaffManager

java.lang.Object
util.StaffManager
public class StaffManager extends Object
The StaffManager class provides functionalities for managing staff members such as doctors, pharmacists, and administrators. It allows adding new staff, updating their details, filtering based on various criteria, and saving data persistently.

      Adds a new staff member to the system.
      Parameters:

      Throws:

    • updateStaff

      public void updateStaff(String staffId, String newName, String newGender, Integer newAge)
      Updates the details of an existing staff member.
      Parameters:
      staffId - the unique identifier of the staff member to update.
      newName - the new name for the staff member, or null to keep the existing name.
      newGender - the new gender for the staff member, or null to keep the existing gender.
      newAge - the new age for the staff member, or null to keep the existing age.
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the staff member is not found or if the role does not support age updates.

    • removeStaff

      public void removeStaff(String staffId)

      Parameters:
      staffId - the unique identifier of the staff member to remove.
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the staff member is not found.
